data.title: Stop and Stare (OneRepublic) by A. Brown, E. Fisher, R.B. Tedder, T. Myers, Z. Filkins on MusicaNeo
data.meta_description: Download Andrew Brown, Eddie Fisher, Ryan B Tedder, Tim Myers, Zachary Filkins Stop and Stare (OneRepublic) sheet music. Digital score of Stop and Stare (OneRepublic).
data.text:
Nick Harper 20 Jan 2017 13:00

Easily learn-able and play-able! Guitar chords actually come as great assistance here, if you're not quite comfortable with the sheet music yet. Love the piano arrangement itself, sounds really a lot like the original even if played solely. The only thing I'd add is some way to convey the string strumming on guitar, which I believe is an important part of the song. Otherwise, the sheet music deserves a 10
